    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>In ceramics, cracking that occurs during firing or cooling due to a rapid changes in temperature; can occur in bisquits or glazed ware.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
